main event: Aloha Airlines flight 789 reported a UFO sighting over the Hawaiian Islands.
interesting points: The object was observed maintaining a westward course and was seen for approximately 15 minutes,The object appeared to have red and blue running lights,The UFO was reported to be above 10,000 feet,The object traveled at a terrific rate of speed for a short period,The sighting was part of reports collected by Project Blue Book.
sighted object: unknown flying object with red and blue running lights
